{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1bd3b44105","title":"在吴旗打给林彪同志的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7629834abc","index":0,"year":1935,"month":11,"day":21,"articleId":"1bd3b44105"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui2","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1943-1949卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui2a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"190e445b63","type":"title","text":"在吴旗打给林彪同志的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"b68c99ceb0","type":"paragraph","text":"林、聂、李、邓：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"3d1cef55a9","type":"paragraph","text":"一、本日已将敌三十五师骑兵团全部击溃、缴获正清查中。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"8dac994cf2","type":"paragraph","text":"二、毛炳文主力尚在廿里铺红德城之线及其以东地区，距我约三、四日行程，但其先遣兵力步骑各一团则距我较近，镇铁城则有奉军一部。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"8cd2f20f91","type":"paragraph","text":"我军坚决准备消灭毛炳文，先遣兵力及求得整理之目的。明二十二日：","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"603332b6c0","type":"paragraph","text":"甲，一纵队移至二道川、三道川一带宿营，派部队向两川上游侦察。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"467c82d98b","type":"paragraph","text":"乙，二纵队在杨城子及吴旗镇原地休息，派部队向头道川上游侦察。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"e4407042dd","type":"paragraph","text":"丙，三纵队在宁包川原地休息。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"eede5cc9e6","type":"paragraph","text":"丁，支队直属队在吴旗镇。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"5851006309","type":"paragraph","text":"四、准备二十二日再休息一天。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"920df8e82d","type":"paragraph","text":"五，加紧筹足三天粮食。","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"669b974a3f","type":"paragraph","text":"六，加紧进行教育解释支队训令。","index":11,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"27da2c2a2c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":12,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"316235291d","type":"paragraph","text":"廿一日十时林、聂：","index":13,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"7e86b614a9","type":"paragraph","text":"我们率二十三分队到二道川口两端十金处之刘河湾，战斗情况如何望告，廿分队留吴旗镇。","index":14,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"b64c518e9c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":15,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"9d5e092b5f","type":"paragraph","text":"廿一日十三时半林、聂：","index":16,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"58e312951b","type":"paragraph","text":"一、明廿二日在吴起镇附近休息一天，一纵队在二道川、三道川、纵队部驻地。","index":17,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"3f1267f542","type":"paragraph","text":"二、第二纵队在吴起镇，杨城子支队部，在吴起镇各加足准备二三天粮食。","index":18,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"ce7bc4ef63","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":19,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"},{"id":"a89ea958cc","type":"paragraph","text":"廿一日十八时","index":20,"publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105"}],"page":{"id":"03c74e823e","publicationId":"wansui2","articleId":"1bd3b44105","start":363,"end":364}}}},"__N_SSG":true}